ases. It also has a strong outreach potential. The animation and a zoomable version of Fig. B.1 are available at https://www.aanda.org Table A.1 is only available at the CDS via anonymous ftp to cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr (ftp://130.79.128.5) or via http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/viz-bin/cat/J/A+A/650/A201, at https://gruze.org/10pc/, and at https://gucds.inaf.it/},
